1、产品入库——填写订货单：
接口：/medicine/add_in_storage_receipt/
接口请求：
[
    {
        "supplier":"供货商",
        "category":"商品类别",
        "goods_name":"商品名称",
        "apply_number":10,
        "unit":"个",
        "estimated_price":2.3,
        "estimated_money":23,
        "applicant": "小王",
        "purpose":"用于治疗感冒",
        "apply_comment":"",
        "apply_datetime": "2019-4-16 10:00:00"
    },
    {
        "supplier":"供货商",
        "category":"商品类别",
        "goods_name":"商品名称",
        "apply_number":10,
        "unit":"个",
        "estimated_price":2.0,
        "estimated_money":20,
        "applicant": "小王",
        "purpose":"用于治疗感冒",
        "apply_comment":"",
        "apply_datetime": "2019-4-16 10:00:00"
    }
    ]
说明：applicant（申请人）是当前登录用户的名称，apply_datetime（申请时间）是当前提交的时间
2、产品入库——订货单审核
1）点击订货单审核，查询出所有的订货单：
接口：/medicine/get_inStorageReceipt/
接口请求：
{
    "all": 1
}
返回数组：
[
    {
        "receipt_no":"订货单单号",
        "supplier":"供货商单位",
        "applicant":"申请人",
        "apply_datetime":"2019-4-16 10:00:00",
        "status":"待审核"
    },
    {
        "receipt_no":"订货单单号",
        "supplier":"供货商单位",
        "applicant":"申请人",
        "apply_datetime":"2019-4-16 10:00:00",
        "status":"未审核"
    }
    ]
###### status：包含三种状态，未审核，已审核，未通过

2）查询
接口：/medicine/get_inStorageReceipt/
接口请求：
{
    "all":0,
    "applicant":"小王",
    "status":1,
    "apply_datetime_start":"2019-4-16 10:00:00",
	"apply_datetime_end":"2019-4-17 10:00:00",
}
# 说明：如果某个字段没有输入查询条件，若字段是字符串类型，则传递""；若是数字类型，则传递-1
# 例如：
{
    "all":False,
    "applicant":"",
    "status":-1,
    "apply_datetime_start":"",
	"apply_datetime_end":"",
}
返回数组：
[
    {
        "receipt_no":"订货单单号",
        "supplier":"供货商单位",
        "applicant":"小王",
        "apply_datetime":"2019-4-16 10:00:00",
        "status":"待审核"
    },
    {
        "receipt_no":"订货单单号",
        "supplier":"供货商单位",
        "applicant":"小王",
        "apply_datetime":"2019-4-16 10:00:00",
        "status":"待审核"
    }
    ]
